t a drawstring — so a drawstring is added, and the silhouette becomes provisional. A chest logo is applied because the garment cannot communicate quality on its own.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"We declined to make any of these compromises.\\\"}]]}]]}]}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"section-y border-b border-[var(--color-border)]\\\",\\\"aria-labelledby\\\":\\\"standard-heading\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"kvrn-container\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"kvrn-label mb-12 md:mb-16\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"standard-heading\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"The standard\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-px bg-[var(--color-border)]\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",\\\"The weight.\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bg-[var(--color-bg)] px-8 py-10 md:py-12\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-[15px] font-light mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"The weight.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Developed around heavyweight loopback terry. Dense enough to have real structural presence. Full specifications on each product page.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",\\\"The hood.\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bg-[var(--color-bg)] px-8 py-10 md:py-12\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-[15px] font-light mb-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"The hood.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Three panels. Seamed to form a dome. No drawstring required. No drawstring installed. The structure is the solution.\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",\\\"The utility.\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bg-[var(--color-bg)] px-8 py-10 md:py-12\\