ing is added, and the silhouette becomes provisional. A chest logo is applied because the garment cannot communicate quality on its own.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"We declined to make any of these compromises.\"}]]}]]}]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"section-y border-b border-[var(--color-border)]\",\"aria-labelledby\":\"standard-heading\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-container\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-label mb-12 md:mb-16\",\"id\":\"standard-heading\",\"children\":\"The standard\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-px bg-[var(--color-border)]\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"The weight.\",{\"className\":\"bg-[var(--color-bg)] px-8 py-10 md:py-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[15px] font-light mb-4\",\"children\":\"The weight.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"Developed around heavyweight loopback terry. Dense enough to have real structural presence. Full specifications on each product page.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"The hood.\",{\"className\":\"bg-[var(--color-bg)] px-8 py-10 md:py-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[15px] font-light mb-4\",\"children\":\"The hood.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"Three panels. Seamed to form a dome. No drawstring required. No drawstring installed. The structure is the solution.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"The utility.\",{\"className\":\"bg-[var(--color-bg)] px-8 py-10 md:py-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[15px] font-light mb-4\",\"children\":\"The utility.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"Interior zipper compartments behind both kangaroo pocket openings. Invisible from outside. Functional in every position.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"The mark.\",{\"className\":\"bg-[var(--color-bg)] px-8 py-10 md:py-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[15px] font-light mb-4\",\"children\":\"The mark.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"One moulded rubber patch on the hood exterior. No chest logo. No sleeve hit. No hang tag with a manifesto. The garment first.\"}]]}]]}]]}]}],\"$L13\",\"$L14\",\"$L15\",\"$L16\"]}],null,\"$L17\"]}]\n11:[\"$\",\"$1\",\"h\",{\"children\":[null,[[\"$\",\"$L18\",null,{\"children\":\"$L19\"}],null],[\"$\",\"$L1a\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"hidden\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"$1b\",null,{\"fallback\":null,\"children\":\"$L1c\"}]}]}]]}]\n1d:I[4431,[],\"OutletBoundary\"]\n1f:I[5278,[],\"AsyncMetadataOutlet\"]\n13:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"section-y border-b border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg-raised)]\",\"aria-labelledby\":\"materials-heading\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-container\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-32 items-start\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-label mb-6\",\"id\":\"materials-heading\",\"children\":\"Materials\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[clamp(28px,3.5vw,48px)] font-light leading-none tracking-tight mb-8\",\"children\":[\"100% ring-spun\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"combed cotton.\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"Nothing else.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed max-w-[380px]\",\"children\":\"Ring-spun yarn is stronger and softer than standard spun cotton — the fibres are continuously twisted and thinned during processing. Combing removes short fibres and impurities. The result is a denser, more durable, cleaner yarn.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed mt-4 max-w-[380px]\",\"children\":\"No polyester. No blends added to reduce cost or improve marketing copy.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"Fibre\",{\"className\":\"flex items-baseline justify-between gap-8 py-4 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)]\",\"children\":\"Fibre\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[14px] font-light text-right\",\"children\":\"100% ring-spun combed cotton\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Weight\",{\"className\":\"flex items-baseline justify-between gap-8 py-4 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)]\",\"children\":\"Weight\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[14px] font-light text-right\",\"children\":\"400 GSM+ heavyweight fleece\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Construction\",{\"className\":\"flex items-baseline justify-between gap-8 py-4 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)]\",\"children\":\"Construction\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[14px] font-light text-right\",\"children\":\"Loopback terry, triple-brushed interior\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Face\",{\"className\":\"flex items-baseline justify-between gap-8 py-4 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)]\",\"children\":\"Face\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[14px] font-light text-right\",\"children\":\"Dense, cold-resist smooth\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Interior\",{\"className\":\"flex items-baseline justify-between gap-8 py-4 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)]\",\"children\":\"Interior\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[14px] font-light text-right\",\"children\":\"Triple-brushed for immediate warmth\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Shrinkage\",{\"className\":\"flex items-baseline justify-between gap-8 py-4 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)]\",\"children\":\"Shrinkage\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[14px] font-light text-right\",\"children\":\"Pre-shrunk to less than 3%\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Care\",{\"className\":\"flex items-baseline justify-between gap-8 py-4 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-muted)]\",\"children\":\"Care\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[14px] font-light text-right\",\"children\":\"Machine wash cold. Air dry.\"}]]}]]}]]}]}]}]\n14:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"section-y border-b border-[var(--color-border)]\",\"aria-labelledby\":\"design-heading\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-container max-w-3xl\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-label mb-12\",\"id\":\"design-heading\",\"children\":\"Design logic\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"Why no drawstring?\",{\"className\":\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr] gap-6 md:gap-12 pb-12 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0 last:pb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[15px] font-light\",\"children\":\"Why no drawstring?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"A drawstring exists because the hood structure is insufficient to maintain its form independently. We built a hood structure — three separate panels seamed to create a self-supporting dome — that does not require external support. The drawstring is therefore unnecessary. Its absence is a consequence of solving the problem correctly.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Why interior zippers?\",{\"className\":\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr] gap-6 md:gap-12 pb-12 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0 last:pb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[15px] font-light\",\"children\":\"Why interior zippers?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"A standard kangaroo pocket holds items that move freely and can fall. An interior zipper pocket holds items that stay. The zipper runs parallel to the pocket opening — invisible from outside, accessible from inside. Both sides. It costs more to produce. It is worth it.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Why no visible branding?\",{\"className\":\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr] gap-6 md:gap-12 pb-12 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0 last:pb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[15px] font-light\",\"children\":\"Why no visible branding?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"Visible branding on a garment performs a function: it communicates that the person wearing it values the label more than the object. KVRN is designed for the opposite — for the person who wants the best version of the thing, not the loudest version of the name. One rubber patch on the hood. Nothing else needs to be said.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"Why 400 GSM when 300 is sufficient?\",{\"className\":\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_3fr] gap-6 md:gap-12 pb-12 border-b border-[var(--color-border)] last:border-0 last:pb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[15px] font-light\",\"children\":\"Why 400 GSM when 300 is sufficient?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\",\"children\":\"At 300 GSM, a hoodie is functional. At 400 GSM+, it becomes structural — it holds its shape, drapes rather than hangs, and maintains its weight and presence after years of wear. The difference is perceptible immediately. There is no argument for the lesser weight.\"}]]}]]}]]}]}]\n15:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"section-y border-b border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-bg-dark)] text-[var(--color-text-on-dark)]\",\"aria-labelledby\":\"position-heading\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-container\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-text-on-dark)]/40 mb-12\",\"id\":\"position-heading\",\"children\":\"The position\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 md:gap-32 max-w-3xl\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"kvrn-label text-[var(--color-text-on-dark)]/60 mb-6\",\"children\":\"KVRN is\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Architectural\",{\"className\":\"py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-text-on-dark)]/10 text-[16px] font-light text-[var(--color-text-on-dark)] last:border-0\",\"children\":\"Architectural\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Heavyweight\",{\"className\":\"py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-text-on-dark)]/10 text-[16px] font-light text-[var(--color-text-on-dark)] last:border-0\",\"children\":\"Heavyweight\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Minimal\",{\"className\":\"py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-text-on-dark)]/10 text-[16px] font-light text-[var(--color-text-on-dark)] last:border-0\",\"children\":\"Minimal\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Functional\",{\"className\":\"py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-text-on-dark)]/10 text-[16px] font-light text-[var(--color-text-on-dark)] last:border-0\",\"children\":\"Functional\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Permanent\",{\"className\":\"py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-text-on-dark)]/10 text-[16px] font-light text-[v